<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA32">
<l>perukoḷiya ceñcaṭaimēṟ piḷḷaip piṟaiyi</l>
<l>ṉorukatirē pōntoḻukiṟ ṟokkun - teriyiṉ</l>
<l>mutaṟkaṇṇāṉ muppuraṅka ḷaṉṟerittāṉ mūvā</l>
<l>nutaṟkaṇṇāṉ taṉmārpiṉ nūl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It resembles the coming [and] flowing of one ray of the very resplendent</l>
<l>child crescent moon on the red matted hair, when one understands [it]</l>
<l>– the thread on the chest of him with an eye on the unaging forehead,</l>
<l>he who set aflame that day the three cities, he who has the first place.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
